Announcement:
As part of our online library management system (LibroX), we believe it is important to add brief yet effective text on the homepage that contains important keywords. This will be an essential aspect of the design of the system, and we will not make this news public because it is part of a university course project.

Example:
We are excited to announce the launch of our new LibroX Application system. Our platform offers an intuitive interface that allows you to search for and borrow books with ease. With a vast collection of books across various genres, we aim to provide an enriching reading experience for all our users. Thank you for choosing our online library management system. Happy reading!
please be informed that the following services has been made available immediately;
• Self-check (Borrowing)
• Book Return (Returning)
• Renewal
• My Library Account
• Fines payment
• Purchase/Buy payment
